# @decision DEC-CI-COMPILE-LINT-LF-001
# All sources in @yakcc/compile are LF-canonical on checkout.
# Mirrors the shave (.gitattributes DEC-CI-SHAVE-LINT-LF-001) and seeds (#418)
# fixes — without an LF pin, Windows checkouts via core.autocrlf=true would
# deliver CRLF and produce phantom format-violations on any PR that
# invalidates the compile-lint turbo cache.

*.ts text eol=lf
*.tsx text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
